Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:07.48,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,270)\fad(600,600)}回\N锅\N肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了  不过我也只能做出这种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厉害  这不是回锅肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好肚子饿扁了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在里面放了一点东西提味  不知你能不能吃出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提味啊  你还真是够认真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  应该说是只有豆酱的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是该说提味凸显得太深了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不如说这个味道越嚼越难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是背道而驰！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:26.47,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N23
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是相当不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:43.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纸上：河童  很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何方妖孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童？  为什么现在要画河童
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还说「很帅吧」…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她这次画的画虽然幻想色彩很强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定某种意义上还算有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这里的巨人指宫崎骏著名电影「幽灵公主」里出场的山神麒麟兽\N原型是日本传说中的巨人「ダイダラボッチ」，传说其一晚上就造出了富士山和琵琶湖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「巨人+河童」之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童  嘿  可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童  河童啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:14.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}河童的发音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAPPA  KAPPA  PA  PA…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就顺着这样开始玩「绘画接龙」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PARASITE是这种生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然画了这个箭头  就是说她在邀请我玩「绘画接龙」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就勉为其难玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是PARASITE呢  TE  TE…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纸上天狗说的话：时间不够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:55.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}上文祐子把寄生虫的日文发音PARASAITO读成了PARASHITE。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且天狗什么的…  她把PARASITE的TO读成TE了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了  是天狗呢  天狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GU  GU  GU…  GU！  骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}天狗的日文发音是TENGU，祐子写成了TENGO。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TENGO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TENGO是什么玩意啊  TENGO！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  是故意写错的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生可不会犯这种幼稚的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她在图上画了天狗  还特地写了文字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总觉得无法理解  这里只能附和她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用GO来接了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:33.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}GOKUU-悟空，画上右下角的字：你给我画小一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倦怠的悟空是怎么回事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啊咧  悟空？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,360)\fs18}GOKUU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我画的应该是天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,360)\fs18}TENGU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  心里想着「GU」却写成了「GO」我能够理解啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下回头得让她请客饮料了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  接下来  是U呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U  U…  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}纸上：我没法画得很好！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胆  不对  是兔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,360)\fs18}UNI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,360)\fs18}USA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牛吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,360)\fs18}USI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个牛也画得太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌头  是舌头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,360)\fs18}SHITA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是TA了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TA  TA  计程车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(395,360)\fs18}TAKUSHII
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什…什么鬼东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是TAXI而是TAXY啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  随便画个东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美绪把寿司（SUSI）倒过来写成SI-SU-。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  连业界用语都用上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就好画了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}超人的日语发音「SUUPAAMAN」的结尾为N，无法再接。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  这样不就输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里  这样做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}祐子在后面加了个假名ZU，成为SUPERMANS。
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.40,-0:00:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:18.35,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,340)\fad(600,600)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好闲啊  关口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  关口  来玩「异口同声」一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我先开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异口同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关口  反正你闲着  偶尔也陪我玩一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  关口…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:06.10,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N24
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:14.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}依旧是5-7-5的俳句格式\N最上川是在山形县的一条河，这里只是为了凑俳句的格式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘写作业  罚站在走廊的  最上川  by祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是忘记写作业了  就被罚站在走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间  要怎样度过  最上川  by祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  有鹿  有只鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么校长要把鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…校长  鹿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  校长他…濒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  鹿煎饼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  大家  校长要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样摔下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爬上去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  DEATH  校长…  DEATH  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…  校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊上一切正常！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从心底发出的最真挚的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是因为想包庇校长  或者说是嫌说明麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只是为了对刚才演出了那场死斗的勇者们致以敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨  过早汇入  最上川  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵…  意义不明
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:08.85,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,600)}10\N円\N足\N球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么  美绪来当裁判哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10円足球不是不需要裁判吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧啧啧  你不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是心情的问题  心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  开球吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都行  攻过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鲨鱼「サメ」和韩语的我爱你开头的发音都是「SA」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:34.17,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N25
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到了一只蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎…慎重地  总之要慎重地行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让这只恶心的恶之根源再次在这个家中滋生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计策…必须想出最优计策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  杀虫剂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是无法一击杀虫  就会有让它逃走的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到它扭曲挣扎的样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  洗涤剂怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矮脚桌的周围洒上洗涤剂用于封住它的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再万无一失地伺机捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  会…会飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是逃走的话这家伙一定会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦飞起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会胡乱地突然飞过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飞到我身上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要是飞向我的脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要是飞到嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飞到嘴里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次就给我来一发ROCK'N'ROLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是棒极了  没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿起这个碗的一瞬间的选项只有「死」和「死掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEATH  or  DIE！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能…只能那样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阪…阪本先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救我  这…这个里面有蟑…  蟑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是蟑螂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊  想要我捉住的话  就把碗打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我就说把碗举起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话怎么捉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在说什么啊  居然要我解除这恶之根源的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是潘多拉之盒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开以后灾祸就会降临啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  不把碗打开的话怎么抓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自己打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么打得开啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的点心是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正是时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士一点都不怕虫  一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  能不能帮我处理一下这个碗里的蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R  R  R  ROCK'N'ROLL！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  那么就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么看我一发解决它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明…我明明是如此认真地烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人却…  这个人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我最讨厌博士了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是骗你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会讨厌博士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  我最喜欢你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.22,0:16:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真拿博士没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  ROCK'N'ROLL开始了！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:08.60,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,400)}数\N到\N10\N的\N话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我热死了  可以出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不是刚刚才进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  数到10就出去怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20㏒√10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我数到10了  可以出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「1…2」不这样数的话不行
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.45,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(600,600)}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  大家都说要去补习班  就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有关口一个人  好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  话说关口你不是说要去补习班来着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:12.68,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N26
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  咖喱怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  马上就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经超级饿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你那里怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钓到大鱼的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是盛宴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  已经差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  超美味超级咖喱完成之卷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边还要煮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做咖喱之前准备好的话就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:06.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本俗语「赤子泣くとも蓋取るな」，意为饭煮到一半不准揭盖。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  毕竟说是「即使小孩哭也不准揭盖」  啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要是带蛋黄酱来就好了  果然吃咖喱就是要放蛋黄酱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋黄…蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你吃咖喱放什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我呕～  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  不是的  这不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你看  我这里还有凉粉可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉粉…开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恶搞北斗神拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙的血是什么颜色的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭的咖喱和米饭都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉粉的话还有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RELEASE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这里还剩下一盒凉粉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一盒吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想让大家轮流着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次是我和美绪不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以麻衣你先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别给我一口全部吃掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多虑了  我又不是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先开动喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呛到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.32,0:21:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  来玩牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  露营会以遗憾收场的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的最后来玩牌  用HAPPY  END来画上句点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人在这种时候不是要喝酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  麻衣你会不会那样想？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也带来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  美绪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿  就是那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了  这样就坏了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管了！  我要喝啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  快停下  会死的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣你还有多的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是苹果酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:09.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原作中出现的安慰祐子的狗狗巴蒂。
