Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:16.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まさか　いや　片思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:15.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an4}両\N思\Nい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やばい！　視線会合っちゃた！！！
